items.how_to_fix:
Terminate TLS on every ingress (cert-manager for automated certs) and redirect HTTP→HTTPS:

```
metadata: {annotations: {cert-manager.io/cluster-issuer: letsencrypt, nginx.ingress.kubernetes.io/ssl-redirect: "true"}}
spec: {tls: [{hosts: [<host>], secretName: <tls-secret>}]}
```

For east-west encryption, adopt a service mesh with mTLS (Istio/Linkerd).
